3001132714866_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=0YCY6l8HNP4Q7kNvgE510MK&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAjkKbRiwdqqkdBvUzAFtgTC1egcvpHq8CK_qvrtuXF2g&oe=6707D951"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "HeroHiddenRealmsTitleCoverArt.png", "id": "3763628287026264", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974558_3763628290359597_6941369554397762485_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=3rrdmvBwvNsQ7kNvgGVu-U8&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB_ZkVJD1O6g674_RuYBTcaqdf0qEVRm0J6-u5f3nNLFw&oe=6707D40A"}, "display_name": "Dungeon of Nekros", "keywords": [], "long_description": "This is a one level demo for the upcoming full game. \n\nYou're alive again...but only for an hour! Temporarily resurrected from the dead, you find yourself in a musty old crypt, buried deep in the bowels of a dark & mysterious dungeon. Your only chance at becoming permanently alive again is to embark on a quest to retrieve the Necronomicon - a terrible & forbidden book desired by the one who resurrected you - Nekros the Necromancer. Discover treasure, fight monsters, & solve the mysteries of the Dungeon of Nekros in this amazing RPG by Hidden Realms.", "short_description": "You're alive again...but only for an hour! Temporarily resurrected from the dead, you find yourself in a musty old crypt, buried deep in the bowels of a dark & mysterious dungeon. Your only chance at becoming permanently alive again is to embark on a quest to retrieve the Necronomicon - a terrible & forbidden book desired by the one who resurrected you - Nekros the Necromancer. Discover treasure, fight monsters, & solve the mysteries of the Dungeon of Nekros in this amazing RPG by Hidden Realms."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://hiddenrealmsvr.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Hidden Realms", "support_website_url": "https://hiddenrealmsvr.com/contact-us", "